<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>The #7 Pencil Charity - The App Cabana</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; background: #0a0e27; color: #fff; }
    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px; }
    .charity-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 60px 40px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .charity-hero h1 { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .charity-hero p { font-size: 18px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); }
    .charity-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .charity-card { background: #1a1f3a; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #333; }
    .charity-card h3 { color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 15px; }
    .charity-card p { line-height: 1.8; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 15px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background: #667eea; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; border: none; font-size: 16px; }
    .btn:hover { background: #764ba2; }
    .impact { background: #1a1f3a; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #333; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .impact h3 { color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .impact-item { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .impact-icon { font-size: 32px; }
    .impact-text { }
    .donation-section { background: #667eea; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; }
    .donation-section h2 { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .donation-buttons { display: flex; gap: 15px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 20px; }
    .donation-btn { padding: 12px 25px; background: #0a0e27; color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #667eea; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; }
    .donation-btn:hover { background: #1a1f3a; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="charity-hero">
      <h1>✏️ The #7 Pencil Charity</h1>
      <p>Supporting education and creativity for underprivileged students</p>
    </div>

    <div class="charity-grid">
      <div class="charity-card">
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>The #7 Pencil Charity is dedicated to providing educational supplies and creative resources to students in need. We believe every student deserves access to quality tools for learning and self-expression.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">Through partnerships with schools and community organizations, we distribute supplies, fund mentorship programs, and support creative initiatives.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="charity-card">
        <h3>Cabana Connection</h3>
        <p>The App Cabana is proud to support The #7 Pencil Charity. A percentage of every sale goes directly to funding educational programs and creative workshops.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">When you create or purchase on The App Cabana, you're helping students discover their potential.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="impact">
      <h3>Our Impact</h3>
      
      <div class="impact-item">
        <div class="impact-icon">📚</div>
        <div class="impact-text">
          <strong>Education Programs</strong>
          <p style="color: #aaa;">Funding art, music, and creative writing classes in underserved schools.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="impact-item">
        <div class="impact-icon">🎨</div>
        <div class="impact-text">
          <strong>Creative Supplies</strong>
          <p style="color: #aaa;">Distributing quality art supplies, instruments, and technology resources.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="impact-item">
        <div class="impact-icon">👥</div>
        <div class="impact-text">
          <strong>Mentorship</strong>
          <p style="color: #aaa;">Connecting students with professional creators and artists for guidance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="impact-item">
        <div class="impact-icon">🌟</div>
        <div class="impact-text">
          <strong>Scholarships</strong>
          <p style="color: #aaa;">Supporting talented students with creative development scholarships.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="donation-section">
      <h2>Support the Mission</h2>
      <p>Every purchase on The App Cabana supports The #7 Pencil Charity. Want to make an additional donation?</p>
      
      <div class="donation-buttons">
        <button class="donation-btn" onclick="alert('Donation feature coming soon!')">Donate $5</button>
        <button class="donation-btn" onclick="alert('Donation feature coming soon!')">Donate $25</button>
        <button class="donation-btn" onclick="alert('Donation feature coming soon!')">Donate $100</button>
        <button class="donation-btn" onclick="alert('Donation feature coming soon!')">Custom Amount</button>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px;">🎭 The App Cabana × The #7 Pencil Charity</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #1a1f3a; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #333; margin-top: 40px;">
      <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 15px;">Learn More</h3>
      <p style="color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 15px;">Want to get involved or learn more about The #7 Pencil Charity?</p>
      <a href="/contact?type=Charity%20Inquiry" class="btn">Get Involved</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
